Gaslamp’s Best Brunch Spot! 🥂✨
📍@rusticrootsd | Gaslamp San Diego
 
Have you been to this incredible rooftop restaurant in San Diego’s Gaslamp neighborhood yet? This group friendly spot is our favorite for a mimosa filled brunch while soaking up the San Diego sun in downtown! ☀️ From their affordable bubble boards that have ALL the garnishes, juices, and toppings to their craft coffee program there are plenty of delicious drinks! 🥂
 
For bites we love their Chicken and Waffles it has the best chili cornbread waffles that are so different! 🧇 The Maryland Blue Crab Cake Eggs Benedict are incredible as well! 🦀 For sweets try their Death By Chocolate Pancakes with marshmallow meringue that is so photogenic and even tastier! 🍫
 
#sdfoodies #sandiego #rusticroot #brunch #breakfast #yum

Rustic Root (@rusticrootsd ) is a two story restaurant located in San Diego’s Gaslamp Quarter that serves modern American fare in an inviting and eclectic atmosphere.  They have rooftop dining where you can enjoy mouthwatering dishes such as their table smoked bone-in rib eye and firecracker shrimp.  They also make some fantastic drinks as well.
